I"Z<div class="p">A gesture of defiance,</div>
<div class="p">Imagine it, and hold</div>
<div class="p">The picture in your memory,</div>
<div class="p">Emblazoned very bold.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Then see it done a thousand</div>
<div class="p">And scores of other times,</div>
<div class="p">With blockheads standing opposite</div>
<div class="p">Resplendent in their crimes.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">They sold our soul to China,</div>
<div class="p">They rent us into halves,</div>
<div class="p">They wrought destruction and decay</div>
<div class="p">With their imported calves.</div>
